}}</ref> He is also a partner in the [[venture capital]] firm, [[Kleiner Perkins Caufield & Byers]], heading that firm's climate change solutions group.<ref name=greenbusiness>{{cite web
|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2007/11/13/BAUCTAV4I.DTL&feed=rss.bayarea
