}}</ref> Gore attended [[St. Albans School (Washington, D.C.)|St. Albans School]] from 1956 to 1965, while his sister Nancy attended [[Holton-Arms School]].<ref name=alum>{{cite web
|url=http://www.stalbansschool.org/home/news_item.asp?id=330 
