  |title = The Mass Media and the Political Agenda
  |year = 2006
  |pages = 210-211
  |place = 
  |publisher = Pearson Education, Inc.
  |url =}}</ref>

Gore graduated with a [[Bachelor of Arts]] [[Academic degree|degree]] in government ''[[cum laude]]'' on June 12, 1969.<ref name=CNNbio>{{cite web
|url=http://www-cgi.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1996/candidates/democrat/gore/
|title=Al Gore Biography
|accessdate= 2008-06-16
