}}</ref> Tipper would also later refer to it as an act of "purification."<ref name=biosen/> Gore also began to work the night shift for ''[[The Tennessean]]'' as an [[Investigative journalism|investigative reporter]] (he worked for the paper from 1971-1976).<ref name=congressbio>{{cite web
|url=http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=G000321 
