}}</ref> His investigations of possible [[Political corruption|corruption]] among members of Nashville's Metro Council resulted in the arrest and prosecution of two councilmen for separate offenses.<ref name=boy>{{cite web
|url=http://www.nashvillepost.com/news/1992/9/17/al_gore_boy_reporter
|title=Al Gore, boy reporter
