|authorlink= 
|coauthors= 
|date=July 10, 1992 
|work= 
|publisher=''[[New York Times]]'' 
}}</ref> Clinton and Gore accepted the democratic nomination at the [[Democratic National Convention]] on July 17, 1992.<ref name=clintonnom>{{cite web
|url= http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CE4DE153AF934A25754C0A964958260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=print
|title=  IN THEIR OWN WORDS; Transcript of Speech by Clinton Accepting Democratic Nomination
|accessdate= 2008-07-10
