|first= William
|authorlink= 
|coauthors= 
|date= July 17, 1992
|work= 
|publisher= ''[[The New York Times]]''
}}</ref><ref name=gorenom>{{cite web
|url= http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CE1D6123AF934A25754C0A964958260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=print
|title=   IN THEIR OWN WORDS; Excerpts From Speech By Gore at Convention
