|coauthors= 
|date=March 2, 1997
|work= 
|publisher= ''[[CNN]]''
}}</ref> In a news conference, Gore stated that, "all calls that I made were charged to the Democratic National Committee. I was advised there was nothing wrong with that. My counsel tells me there is no controlling legal authority that says that is any violation of any law." <ref name=PBSmoney>{{cite web
|url=http://www.pbs.org/newshour/bb/white_house/march97/fund_3-6.html
