}}</ref> 

Gore faced an early challenge by former [[New Jersey]] senator [[Bill Bradley]].<ref name=announce2000/> Bradley was the only candidate to oppose Gore and was considered a "fresh face" for the White House."<ref name=boyhoodhome>{{cite web
|url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/stories/1999/09/08/president.2000/bradley/
|title= Bradley returns to boyhood home to launch fall campaign
