}}</ref> Gore challenged Bradley to a series of debates which took the form of "town hall" meetings.<ref name=townhall>{{cite web
|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C06EFD71539F933A15753C1A96F958260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=print
