|date=March 8, 2000
|work= 
|publisher= ''[[USA Today]]''
}}</ref> Gore eventually went on to win every primary and caucus and in March of 2000, secured the Democratic nomination.<ref name=dropout>{{cite web
|url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article.aspx?ref=99867
|title=Bradley, McCain Drop Out of Race
